NOTE ON DWARF FORTRESS:
This repository contains only the web infrastructure (session manager, container
definitions, frontend). Dwarf Fortress itself is NOT included and is subject to
Bay 12 Games' own license terms. You must obtain it separately from
https://www.bay12games.com/dwarves/ and comply with those terms when running it
on a server. The classic "free" build of Dwarf Fortress is available at no
charge but remains the property of Bay 12 Games. This infrastructure is designed
for personal/non-commercial use consistent with Bay 12 Games' licensing.
